Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤离奥布？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是职业军人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布被攻陷只是时间问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道闭合 确认连接弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人 大家一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不可以留下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服从国家 服从军队讨伐敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是理所当然的 是无可厚非的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望 这样的战争早一天结束
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.57,0:00:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首上仰20 罗恩格林待命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赶紧起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲和你分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布和世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不会听从他们的摆布
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
