Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.58,0:02:51.55,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord2\shad0\1a&HFF&\3a&H00&\an3\fs60}动荡的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B船体 距离200
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C船体 距离230
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轴线正常 对接轴线吻合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持对接姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正误差
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接导航仪 各乘员待命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对接最后阶段 确认本地控制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全站点接合正常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.47,0:03:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉号对接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉小姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情绪稳定多了 一言难尽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在 也不忍心对她太过严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 问题是接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉号迄今为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是作为来往于赫利奥波利斯的运输舰使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然载有机动战士和武装
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但与大天使号不可相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成5个部分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有核心部分跑空间站吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.81,0:04:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这办法效率不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.25,0:04:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大天使号好像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大天使号 像它才对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都产自曙光社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把宇域图显示出来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.55,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃里卡·西蒙斯主任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊 少校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我国的机动战士第一次上宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了我怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们的当前位置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如二位所知 L5是PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L3是阿尔狄弥斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲和你分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.67,0:05:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去L4的卫星群？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉号和大天使号眼下物资充足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并非用之不竭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.79,0:05:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是水 一旦缺水会很成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L4的卫星群自开战以来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接连受损 遭到遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作为水的补给源 相当合适
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 那里不是尤尼乌斯7号
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L4还有几颗 运转中的殖民卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久前 据报有可疑组织把那里当作巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特还专门前往调查过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居民已经全部疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卫星设施仍然完好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就是它了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.23,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你确定这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.80,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 不只是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有另一位朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少校…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布战场上的事我也看在眼里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况说特殊确实特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎你以前穿什么军服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但毕竟今后我们不排除
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能 和扎夫特战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟奥布的战斗不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有那种觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是帕德里克·萨拉的儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的儿子重要吗 阿斯兰是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军人开小差的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你想像得严重的多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更何况头头是自己的亲爹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有坚定的信念 打不了仗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是推翻它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里可能那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且他和基拉不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正规军人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丑话说在前头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想当战友 给我个信你的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.87,0:07:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 到底怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.59,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奥布…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在PLANT和地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见的 听见的 让我想了许多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是错是对…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己明白了什么 没明白什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我到现在还不能确定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我想要的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们想要的是同一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我现在唯一可以确定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.27,0:08:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年老成 看不出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比基拉懂事多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布托付我们的东西 份量不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠这么两艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说 近乎于不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 既然决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火种再小 也不会让它熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT有人也有相同想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:08:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.69,0:09:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个粉红头发的公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是阿斯兰的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在正在被通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为叛国罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们欲去往何处？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲得到什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战场上 我们所爱的人每天都在付出生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们究竟要让这样的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续到何时才会满足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让战争早日结束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可轻信拉克丝·克莱茵的言论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她串通地球军 向敌人出卖军事机密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人希望发生战乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 究竟是谁导致了这样的事态
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家好好回想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然人对待我们这些来自于他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却进化了的人种
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:10:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因嫉妒 实施了数不清的迫害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时 贪婪地窃取我们的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自PLANT理事国建立伊始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强加于我们各种无理而苛刻的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们主张权益
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却收到了一颗核弹的回应！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们而言 这是一场不能输的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失败 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待我们的是越发黑暗的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的人们和我们是同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不是进化的种群
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,试问　强制婚姻政策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何无法增加我们的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样有何资格称是进化了的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被充满恶意的信息所骗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:11:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经是 区别于自然人的不同人种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时的技术难题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必将被我们的睿智攻克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:25.40,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}夜在波光中摇摆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:40.31,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}哀愁静静伫立
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:47.42,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}翠绿的海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:54.99,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}鲜美的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:10:01.74,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}若能一直守候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:08.71,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}带着纯洁的心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:28.27,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}暗海与天空彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:42.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}有处与世无争的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:49.37,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}是谁告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:57.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}谁却也无法抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:05.92,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}或者它只存在于人们心中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:12.44,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}平息浊流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:20.32,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}滋润大地万物的歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:26.84,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}现在又在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:34.44,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}一定只有自己亲手去获得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:41.70,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}一定　会有　一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:47.27,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1\an9}能与你手牵手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止战争 寻求其他途径
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是我们追求的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的女儿仍逍遥法外
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.60,0:11:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们打算让这耸人听闻的广播
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.27,0:11:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜失去心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢得的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真会是幸福的所在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍痛战斗在当下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并期待和平灿烂的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.39,0:11:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议长看来 拿拉克丝·克莱茵办法不多
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.33,0:11:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 召集我们回国不会为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我至今无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会是叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多人正像你这样想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他们才选择了她 克莱茵派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们可是军人 怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争中交织着各种人的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么才是必须与战的 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看走了眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要转移是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.84,0:12:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么新消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚和奥布受到地球军袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥布的质量加速器被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.51,0:12:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利亚的被夺回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说 维多利亚有扎夫特重兵防守
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.43,0:12:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军使用了新型机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须加紧行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 西格尔大人他？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军 维多利亚基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.60,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 打得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名不虚传啊 萨瑟兰上校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 是强袭短剑的性能了得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿兹拉尔大人在奥布的苦战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要因为某些意外因素
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:14:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有许多课题亟待解决
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 没想到有灾祸 禁忌 劫掠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会那么费力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不容小觑的国家啊 奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想法匪夷莫测
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无非是想四处周旋渔翁得利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个卑鄙的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个国家的科技有PLANT的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 说不定那两架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是扎夫特的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 得想办法对付
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知能搞到手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以您决定亲赴宇宙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我看的话那架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是核能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没确凿证据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那样的作战能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:15:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用常规手段不可能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中子干扰器出自调整人之手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们造出使其无效的装置也不足为奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果当真如此 事态就令人忧虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 怀疑我这个国防产业理事的眼光？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 在下怎敢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底我们是弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付那些用尖牙利爪武装起来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么关起来要么拴住 否则谈何安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好的待在宇宙里 还如此猖獗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就自个儿跑一趟吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的幕后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蓝色宇宙盟主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩尔达·阿兹拉尔的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而如今的PLANT 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被掌控在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主张调整人种族论的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕德里克·萨拉手中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也基本结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回大天使号吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实哪边都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里M-1机满为患了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占用一点时间 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 拜托别走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？谁的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草雉号起飞前 父亲大人给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你不是一个人」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「还有兄弟」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…我也 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双胞胎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没回祖国了吧 伊扎克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.52,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家见见父母 也好让他们放心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.48,0:19:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身边 你就是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管放心吧 芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…总之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单凭这张照片没法断定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个抱着孩子的人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你是兄弟 那我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在多想也没用 卡嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算是那样 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉的父亲是乌兹米大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 不用留下陪她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起 反而容易胡思乱想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
